item.title: #189 - Pastor John David Terry
item.description: People disappear all the time and murder victims get labelled incorrectly as runaways. But sometimes its voluntary, people want to start a new life unburdened by their past. Such a plan this week required a body so that the runaway would not be looked for by authorities and to pay out insurance to their family. What’s a little murder between an employer and employee? . . . This week we discuss: Murder, Motive, Arson, Dismemberment, Larceny, Insurance Fraud Sources: https://murderpedia.o...
